Roger Davies (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Davies_(actor) 0 Roger Davies is a British television and film actor. He is best known for playing the character Vinnie Rodriguez in the Nickelodeon UK series Renford Rejects. In 2018, he featured in Netflix/Bad Robot's The Cloverfield Paradox.
